With some new planet packs popping up recently, and based on the New Horizons mission coming alive next year, it's made me think how it'd be nice to have some small dwarf planets to visit out beyond and in the vicinity of Eeloo (like Eris). Maybe also some small rocky worlds between Duna and Jool where Dres is (like Ceres).

That is all.
